  "texts": [
    "21 using Quirk [48].",
    "As mentioned at the end of Sec.",
    "17) is satisfied, we can see a much larger ratio between the qubits labeled with the red arrows and qubits labeled with the green arrows, which shows the full advantage of this work's approach.B Action of our protocol when the input state is not |0 n ⟩ Our state preparation procedure acts on n data qubits and uses a number ℓ = O(N) of ancilla qubits.",
    "It implements a unitary operation U on the n + ℓ qubits that sends |0 n ⟩ |0 ℓ ⟩ → |ψ⟩ |0 ℓ ⟩, that is, all the ancillae begin and end in |0⟩.",
    "However, if the same unitary is performed on a state |z⟩ |0 ℓ ⟩ for some z ̸ = 0 n (or more generally, a state which is a superposition of all z ̸ = 0 n), it will no longer be the case that all ancillas are reset to |0⟩."
  ]
